Distribution ( Fig. 140 ). Present in Honduras , Guatemala , and Mexico , in the following ecoregions (
Dinerstein et al . 2017
): Pine-oak forests of the Central America, Dry forests of the Central Depression of Chiapas , and Humid forests of the Sierra Madre of Chiapas . Broad altitudinal distribution: 315 to 2512 masl .
